<h1>Welcome to Harwood Unified Union School District</h1>

<p>The Harwood Unified Union School District provides a rigorous, innovative and student-centered educational experience in a welcoming and inclusive environment while ensuring equity, effectiveness, and efficiency.  We will partner with our community to achieve our vision for excellence.</p>

<p>To learn more about HUUSD, please peruse the <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1yJrbRrxN-QUFQ2cySU8Pz8EJz2jATKP1" target="_blank">HUUSD Mission</a> and our <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B2uQwDkbPKEVaG5TWGxGRzU0UlE" target="_blank">Action Plan</a>.</p>
